{
  "stem": "25027.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We used to see many atrocities on the roads, on the small roads in the villages when we liberated some of them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dead women and children [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] just laying in the-- in the-- frozen to death.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People were killed for no reason.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the ones that survived explained to us what happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of them were taken out to be drained of blood-- at least, this is what they told us-- to get the blood for the German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We found a Russian lieutenant that they interrogated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What they did is they took off his boots, and they put his feet in a pail of water, and his feet were frozen.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was frozen to death like that outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That I call an atrocity.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We found areas where a group of women nurses in their uniforms was slaughtered with the doctors.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they had definitely had a Red Cross sign there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the Ger-- by who else?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That I couldn't tell you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There might have been some-- some Jewish nurses or doctors, yes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They responded the same way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We caught some Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If they were SS, we didn't hold on to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We shot them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of them were hung.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It depends.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of them were brought in, interrogated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the captain used to say, shoot the son of a bitch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Look, it was war, and there were atrocities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was only once in a case where I had to shoot somebody.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, seeing his face, the captain ordered me to do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But otherwise, I try to stay away from it, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] though I hated them with all my being.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
